\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 And you're married aren't you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Landscove. Near Newton Abbot.
