\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Can you remember the year of your marriage?
