\insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 teenth, 1897.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Where were you born?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 In Trumpatory - Issington. Trumpator. That's right. About - three mile out from Ashburton.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 How many years did you live in the house where you were born?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Oh seven year say. 'Cos I wasn't very old, can't remember. Seven years.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Where did you move then? Did you move to another house?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Lonestom.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Where's that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Same parish. Only about two miles further away.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 How long did you live there? Until 1918?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 No. About - about five year. Then we moved to - Oldertown.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Is that in the same area?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Same.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Do you remember why the family made these moves? Why did your parents change addresses like this?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 You can't remember?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 How many brothers and sisters did you have?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 I've had six brothers and sisters.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Can you remember whether they were older or younger than you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 They're all younger than - older than me.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 You were the youngest were you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 I'm the youngest.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 How many brothers did you have?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 One. One brother.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Five sisters?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 They'm all - they'm all gone, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Do you remember roughly what ages they were when you were born?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Well say fourteen. Ten. Twenty, thirty, like that. Near enough, I can't reckon in - I can't mind.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Was there any brother or sister quite close to you in age?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 No.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 They were all a lot older than you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 How old was your father when you were born, do you remember?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Was forty-five.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Your mother was forty-five and your father was forty-five as well?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 That's about it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Can you remember how old your oldest sister would be, about thirty did you say?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Now -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 How old would the oldest child be when you were born?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Oh about thirty.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Where did your father come from, do you remember?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Newton St Cyrus way.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Is that in Devon as well?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 No, that's in Exeter district.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 What was his occupation?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Farm labourer.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Did he have any other job before or after he became that? Was he always a farm labourer or did he change his job at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 No, he did no other jobs.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 He didn't have any sort of casual or part time jobs as well?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Yes, he did sometimes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 What kind of jobs would those be?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Well, it was on a farm the same. You see, working on a farm the same. And he's working for himself you see. Piecework see.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 On top of the normal working day would this be?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Yes. When he wasn't working for - the farmer he'd work himself. 'Cos I - I used to work with him. When I left school.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 What kind of things would you do?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Driving horses.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 This would be the piecework would it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Oh no, it wouldn't be - I mean, it's when we was working on a farm constant, and he left the farm and 
we shifted from Oldertown - he used to work in a farm called Smollercombe. See, he shifted from there, I - and I left school when went in there.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 How old were you when you left school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Thirteen. And when he left there, he went down a place called
 Southbrook, Bovey Tracey. Southbrook. Bovey Tracey. Southbrook. Bovey Tracey.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 So you moved from Oldertown?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Oldertown.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Then you went to Bovey Tracey?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 That's right.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Until 1918 did you stay in Bovey Tracey?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 I joined the - joined the - Army from there. And went across in France in - 1916.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 But your parents moved to Bovey Tracey about 1912?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 My parents - me parents lived at Bovey Tracey.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 So you changed house about four times between 1897 and 1918?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Did your father work as a farm labourer all the time?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 All - all the time, all his life.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Do you remember your father ever being out of work at all?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 No, never out of work in they days.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 How old was your mother when you were born, you said forty-five didn't you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Do you remember where she came from?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Up that way. Exeter district.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 So she was quite near to where your father was?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 That's right.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Did she have any jobs before she got married?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Well I couldn't tell you, I don't know, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13265840\charrsid9705256 Did she work after she was mar}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 ried?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 No. Home. Looking after the home.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 In the afternoon did you say?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Pardon?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Did you say in the afternoon?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 No, looking after her home, they didn't go out in they days.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Did she ever have any part time jobs at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 No. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 So you can't remember her working ever, apart from looking after the children?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Never worked out.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 I suppose it would be a full time job anyway?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 What was life like at home when you were a child, how many rooms would there be in the house at Oldertown?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Well two - two bedrooms. And two downstairs.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Would all the children be in one bedroom?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Yes. All - that's right, well we wasn't - you see, they was growed up, as one goes off so the others take his place.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 So when you were a child some of the brothers and sisters would be not living in the house?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 No, they'd be gone out in service then.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Did all your sisters go into domestic service?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Yes, that's right. Cooks and - servants.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Were there any reception rooms in the house?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 No. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 What were the two rooms downstairs then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Oh about the -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 What kind of rooms would they be?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Didn't - didn't have no - mats like - like this in they days. Well used to have canvas I think, canvas like.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 What would the two rooms downstairs be called?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Oh kitchen. And the back kitchen.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 What was the difference between the front kitchen and the back kitchen?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 The back kitchen where you do your work in. In the front kitchen where you go and sit down when the work's done.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Did anyone besides your parents and brother and sisters live in the house?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 You said you had lodgers?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Oh lodgers, yes, yes. That's when there was houses - houses being built.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Where did these lodgers come from?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Torquay.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 They'd stay all the time would they in the house?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Yes? They - they stop - come - Monday morning and - and stop for Friday nights.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Did you ever have any neighbours?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 No neighbours.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Was this a farm cottage?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 That's right. And the farm was about - nearly a quarter of a mile away from the cottage.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Were you and all your brothers and sisters living in the house at the same time or had they gone away?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 They was all gone in service. I was the only one left home.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Were there any relatives living at the house in Oldertown?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 No. Only me, father and mother.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Were all the houses you lived in farm cottages?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Yes. Yes. All the lot.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Did you have lodgers in any of the other houses?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 No, only that one.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Did your mother pay anyone to help in the house at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 No, no, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 There was nobody living in to help?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Was the washing done at home or was it sent out?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Yes, at home.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Where would that be done? In the kitchen?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 In the kitchen. The back kitchen.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Did your mother or father ever make or mend the family clothes?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 They - no - used to make some.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 What kind of clothes?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Well - what they couldn't afford to pay in they days.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 What kind of clothes would they make?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Well -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Trousers?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Shir - shirts. Pants.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Did they ever make their own clothes? Was it your mother who made them?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Yes. Me mother. Only me mother.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Did she ever make your father's clothes?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Only mend it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 She wouldn't make them?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Where would you get your clothes?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Bovey Tracey. Bovey Tracey.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Is that nearby?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 That - three mile from - where we used to live.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 What kind of place was this where you bought your clothes in Bovey Tracey?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 A shop.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 A tailor's shop?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 A tailor's shop.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Would he clothes be new or second}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13265840\charrsid9705256  }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 hand?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 New some of 'em.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Did you ever get any second}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13265840\charrsid9705256  }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 hand ones?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Yes, I expect, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Did your sisters in service ever send money back from their job to your mother and father?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 How often would you buy new clothes, or your mother buy new clothes for you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Oh say once in four year.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 So you'd have to make do?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 That's right. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 What about boots and shoes?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Well - as long as they'd last.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Children's feet tend to outgrow shoes don't they?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Would you wear shoes or boots in those days?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Boots in they days. No shoes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 What about your father and mother, did they have to go four years without new clothes?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Mother used to go with me.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Did she have many clothes or did she mend the ones she'd already got?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Oh just - ordinary clothes they had. Like women do.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Did she like making clothes and things?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Yes.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Did she make dresses and things like that for herself?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Did your father ever help your mother with any of the jobs in the house do you remember?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 No. He weren't no - he weren't nothing for indoors, he's like me.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Did he never help to cook or anything?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 No, no, mother - mother had to do it herself.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 So she would do the washing up and make the fires?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 That's right, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 What about decorating, did he ever help with decorating the cottage?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 No. Weren't much done in they days. Not decorating.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 How about repairs?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Well the - the farmer had to do that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Did your father ever help you dress at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 How about undress?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Meself.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 You'd do it yourself?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 From a very early age?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 When I was old enough.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 How old would that be?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Oh - oh about six years.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Did your father ever bath you do you remember?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Did your mother?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 When I was young. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Your mother would do that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 That's right.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Would your father ever read to you do you remember?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 He read - read the Bible. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 He'd be the one who read the Bible to you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Yes, mother too.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Would he ever tell you stories?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Yes. With the Bible. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Would he ever read anything else or tell you any other stories?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 No. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Did your father ever take you out without your mother do you remember?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Would your mother go out with you very much?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 I used to go out with mother.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Where would you go then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Yes, we used to go - chapel every Sunday. Three times a day. Wesleyan chapel.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 How far away was that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 That was - two mile, more.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 This if from Oldertown is it?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 From Oldertown.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Did your father ever look after you when she was out, when your mother was out?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Did you ever have any tasks that you had to carry out regularly at home to help your mother and father?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Yes. I - I used to carry milk - before I went to school to these gentlemen's houses.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Which gentlemen are these?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Them - Lancaster Show when the houses was building.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 How far away were those houses?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 About a quarter of a mile, half a mile from - from where I lived.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 What kind of work did these gentlemen do?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 He - Torqyay, he was a - a parson. A church parson, he used to come up there for a holiday.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 That was his summer house was it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 That's right. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 That was just the one house that was being built?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Yes, there was two or three being built the same time, well this is the house that I used to go to.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 You used to deliver the milk for him?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 That's right, every morning.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 From what age would that be, before you went to school you say?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 That was before I went to school. And then I had to go two mile to school after that. And be in school be nine o'clock.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 So what time would that mean you getting up?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 I should have to get up about quarter past seven mornings, half past seven perhaps.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Would there be anything else you did to help?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 
Yes, I used to go round see father's rabbit gins before I went to school. They used to use rabbit traps in they - yes, and mole gins. I used to go all round his mole gins afore I went school. Well - catching moles. Moles. Yes. Them little black things.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Did you do this regularly?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 That's right. Father -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 What did you use the moles for?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Father used to sell 'em so much a - a tail. Penny a tail perhaps for catching, and he used to skin 'em and sell the skins.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 What did they used the skins for?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Well they made coats of 'em and that. Moleskins, yes. Used to in they days.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Was it quite big around Devon, mole catching?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Yes, we - you - you see the runs and tell 'em in the runs. I've caught hundreds. Yes, hundreds and hundreds I've caught.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Does it still happen nowadays?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 There isn't much done to it now. I used to do it, father used to get penny a tail. For the farmer.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 He'd sell them to the farmer would he?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 
That's right, he'd have to cut off their tail and put 'em in a tin. And - and when he got so many he would - the farmer'd be there to count what he had you see. And he'd give him penny for each tail that he had.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 What other things would you do, you say you looked after the moles and looked after the rabbit traps and things?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Yes, that's - that's right. Oh - well I didn't have much time for much else. Only used to get the stick when I us
ed to go to school in they days. That's more than they get now.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 How long did you carry on these tasks, did you do them after you left school?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Oh no, no, no, no, because I went out farm house then.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 You say your brother and sisters were all away by this time?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Yes, my brother - was working in - in a mine.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 What was he doing in the mine?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Yes, in the tin mines, a miner.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Was he very much older than you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 He wasn't home, he was away married when I was home.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 So he's quite a bit older than you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Oh - lot - yes, lot older.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 So you wouldn't remember anything of your older brother and sisters looking after you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Oh no, no, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Or vic}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13265840\charrsid9705256 e}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 
 versa, you helping them in any way?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 No, I wasn't old enough.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Were you expected to go to bed at a certain time in your schooldays?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Oh I went to bed by eight o'clock I think.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Did that ever change, were you supposed to be in bed by eight o'clock all the way through your schooldays?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Did your mother or anybody else help to put you to bed?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Oh I - I went meself when I was old enough.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 How old would that be?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Oh, about eight or ten - six or eight perhaps.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 You'd have your own room du}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13265840\charrsid9705256 r}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 ing these times?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Yes, I used to sleep in bed to - bedroom meself.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Where would the lodger be?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 He'd be in another place.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Another room?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 You said you only had two rooms?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Yes, well the - the - the - I used to - fence it off, you know what I mean, fence it off in they days.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 The room itself?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Divided down the middle?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Divided off see, if you had anybody else coming. 'Course father and mother used to sleep in be theirself.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Did you have the just one lodger at a time?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Only one, yes, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 
Was this sort of common around the neighbourhood? Did farm cottagers often have lodgers? Was there much house building going on in the countryside at that time?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 No, was only a farm cottage.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Were there any houses being built?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 About three. About three up on the hill being built then.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Where would all the other men lodge?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Oh I couldn't say.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 What room did you bath in?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Down by the kitchen fire. In a small tin bath.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 How often did you bathe?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Oh once a week in they days.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 What day of the week would it be?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Well about - Friday nights.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Why Fridays, any reason?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Friday night.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Any special reason for Friday?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Well - end of the week.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 When did you have clean clothes to put on? Would that be Friday as well?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 When would you have clean clothes to put on?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 After you'd bathed.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Where would the family have their meals?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 In the - kitchen.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 In the front kitchen or the back kitchen?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Back kitchen.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Were there any occasions when they ate in another room?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 No. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Always in the back kitchen?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Back kitchen.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Where would your mother cook? Would that be in the back kitchen as well?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Yes, that's right.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 What kind of equipment would she have, cooking equipment?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 A stove in they day, coal stove in they days, that's all.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Could you tell me a little bit about the details of the meals during the day, when was breakfast eaten?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 At breakfast we'd be - fried potatoes an
d bacon. That was before - that was - about eight - eight o'clock, half past eight. Eight to half past.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Who would be there at that time? Who would eat at that time, would your father and mother both be there at breakfast?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 No, father was gone work, he went to work - seven o'clock. Me and me mother -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 He wouldn't come back for breakfast?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 No, he used to take it in a bag.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 What kind of things would he take with him?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Well, well like a haversack.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 What kind of food would he eat for breakfast?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Bread and cheese and cider. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 So there'd be just you and your mother for breakfast really?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 That - that's right.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Where would you get the bacon from, would you get it from the farm?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 No, from the grocer. Or butcher. Butcher. Butcher. But - the but - butcher.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Where would the butcher be, in the nearest town, village?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Used to come around. Yes, come around from Bovey Tracey.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Would the lodger have breakfast with you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 No, he had it for - afore I did.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Did he used to have breakfast though?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 He used to have tea when - when I come home. In the night.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 You had breakfast about eight o'clock and it was just you and your mother?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 What about the midday meal, did you have a midday meal?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 
No, I used to take mine in a - in a - in a bag. There were no hot food in school in they days. I used to take a meat pasty or a jam pasty or anything baked.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 What time would you have tea?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 What time did I get home? Used to come out of school four o'clock. And I used to get home about half past. In the night.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Would you eat then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Have our tea then.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 What would you have for tea?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Well - mm - cake and butter I expect.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Was your father in by this time?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 No, he wasn't, he didn't used to leave work fore five. He - time he done his horses it would be six time he got home. Six o'clock.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Would he have a meal when he came in?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 He'd have a meal when he come home.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 What would that be called?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Well perhaps fry. Fried bacon and - an egg perhaps, potatoes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Would you eat again then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Oh no, no, 'cos I'd had mine, all depends whether I was hungry or no, I would if I was hungry.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 So you'd have breakfast and tea?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 And a midday snack?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Your father would have bread and cheese, would that last him all day, the bread and cheese?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 And father would have bread and cheese and cider.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Then he'd come back and have a meal at night?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 That's right. That's right.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Would your mother eat tea with you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Yes, mother would.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Would she have an evening meal?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 That's right, no, no meal - evening meals, only tea in those days.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Except for your father?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Yes, that's right.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Did you - what did you call that when your father came in?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Oh used to call that supper.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 But you didn't have supper. Do you remember whether - what kind of things you'd drink for breakfast and tea?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Tea. Cup of tea.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Did you ever have any cider with meals?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Not at - no, only in his work.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 You wouldn't have cider in the house?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Did you have anything different on Saturday or Sunday?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 No. Of course in Saturday and Sunday he'd be home, have a baked dinner in they days.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 What time of day would you eat that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Oh one o'clock.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Was this both Saturday and Sunday or just Sunday?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Yes, 'cos Sundays you see he'd be home dinner, and then I should go to chapel. Well in the afternoon and the evening.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Would he work on Sunday mornings?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 
No, he'd have to go down - perhaps an hour in the morning to do his horses and then when become home in the afternoon he'd have to go down again and do his horses - half - hour perhaps. In they days.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Did he have to do the cows and things like that as well?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 No, only horses.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 What kind of things would he do with the horses?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Well clean 'em down and feed 'em. Clean 'em out.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Was it a livestock farm or crops or what?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 All round - all round farm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 But he had special responsibility for the horses did he?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 That's right, that's all he had to look after, the horses and do the - work on the on the fields.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 What kind of work was that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Well ploughing or -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 With the horses again?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Three, he had three horses.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Would you eat anything different on a Sunday?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 You wouldn't do nothing Sundays in they days.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 But would the food be different on a Sunday?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 You'd have to feed 'em. You'd feed 'em on a Sunday.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 What did the baked dinner consist of?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Potatoes. Greens, meat. Apple sauce if you had any.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 You'd have this about one o'clock?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 That's right.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 What time would you have breakfast on a Sunday?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 No, about nine o'clock.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Your father wouldn't be present for that either?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 No, he'd be about his horses.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 What about tea and supper on a Sunday, would they be the same? Would you have tea and supper on a Sunday?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 That's right.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Both?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Yes. Tea, about five. And perhaps - perhaps when us come home from chapel us may have a little bit of a supper then. Cold meat.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 You'd have supper on Sunday as well?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Yes. Along with mother and father.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 So Sunday was really the only time you sat round the table together as a family?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 That's right. Yes. That's right. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Where would the lodger be?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Oh he - he'd be gone home, Torquay.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Did your mother or father ever bake their own bread?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Did she make her own jam?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Used to make her own jam.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 What would she use for that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Different sort of jam. Apple jam or blackberry.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 How about bottled fruit or vegetables?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Oh weren't - oh weren't nothing in they days, only pickled onions.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 You'd do pickled onions?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Yes, that's right, there weren't no tins of fruit like there is today.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Did she bottle her own?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 No. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Did she ever make any sort of wines or medicines?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 No. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 How about beer, was any beer brewed for the family?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Bills?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Beer?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 No, no. No. Only cider.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Did you brew that yourself?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 No, no, whoever - the farmer. See?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 What happened there, did he sort of bring it down for you or did you collect it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 No, father used to have a little keg - he'd order about three or four pints. And what he didn't dri
nk in the day he'd bring home of a night if there was any left. All depends on the weather.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 This was mainly for him rather than the family?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 That's - yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Did you ever grow your own vegetables and fruit?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Yes. Grow - grow all - grow - grew our own.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Where would you grow those?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 That's in the garden.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 You had your own garden?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 That's right. Used to - put potatoes out in the field. Farmers field.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 You used to use their land as well?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 That's right, tell 'em - tell 'em when the field where the farmers - potatoes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Any other crops you'd do that for?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 No, no, the other crops in the garden.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 What kind of things would you grow in the garden?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Greens, carrot and parsnips. Beetroot. All different things.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Did you have anything like hens or pigs?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Had pigs. Yes, father used to keep pigs in they days. Just one in and out you know or -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Where would you keep that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 In a pigs house, outside.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Would that be yours or the farmer's?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Th
e - belonged to the farm you see. Only that was a privilege keeping a pig in - in the place. You get - get a pig about ten or twelve score and then you'd have a - somebody come and kill 'em see. And - put in half of 'em and - and - have the other half for
 to pay for the barley meal what you've bought.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 You wouldn't have anything like deep freeze or anything in those days?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Oh no, no, no. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 How long would a pig last?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Oh he'd last afore he's gone I mean - you know, I - I couldn't say.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Would you eat pork more than other meat?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Yes. Just about the same as ordinary meat for a change you know. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 You'd have to get the other meat from the butcher?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 We had a butcher that come around, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 How often a week would you eat meat, do you remember?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Well every day if us could get it. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 So by and large you ate a fair amount of meat during the week?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Yes, yes. Yes, of course it's cheaper then.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Do you remember going mushrooming or anything like that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 No. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Would you ever have tinned meat?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 No. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 No tinned vegetables?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 No, no, no, wasn't about then.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Did you ever have a goat?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Or hens?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 No. No. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Who would look after the pig then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Me father - me father would feed 'em mornings and he'd feed 'em dinnertime, and he' feed 'em again in the night when he come home.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 How would he feed them in the dinnertime if he was out in the fields? Where was the pig kept?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Our pig - in our cottage or - h
ouse near - near our cottage. Mother get it all ready, and father would feed 'em when he come home in - in ordinary bucket.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 You only ever had the one pig at a time?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 That's right.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Did you ever get any extra meat from poaching?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 No, only rabbit he was caughting. Extra - you know what I mean.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 What would you do with the rabbits when you caught them?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Well - mother - mother would cook it. Bake it or stew it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 The farmer knew about this?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Oh he - he had a - that was a priv
ilege, farmer would know it, 'cos that was a privilege on the farm in they days, catch a rabbit or anything.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 So would the farmer know or not?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Well all the same if he did, wouldn't matter, he wouldn't make no odds. No. That was your privilege see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Did you get any more privileges like this?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 
Yes, they - they used to - yes, they used to get their milk - so much milk every day give them from the farm. See, about - say - perhaps a quart. That was a privilege.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Would that be enough for the day?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 So really you got a lot of your food and drink by being near the farm didn't you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 That's right, yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Do you ever remember seeing your mother eat less food so that the family could have more?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 No, no, no, no, mother -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Did your father ever have more than the others?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 No. No. Generally had enough.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Were you allowed to talk during meals?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 I forget that, I know father used to - say grace and mother. You know, when you was sat at the table.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 But after you'd said grace could you speak?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Afore you had your food. And after. Yes. No, before and after.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 While you were eating your food were you meant to be quiet or could you talk if you wanted to?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Oh no, it - it wouldn't do for you to talk. You'd have a clip on the ear if you did.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Why was that do you think?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Oh they would - they would in they days.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Could you choose what you wanted to eat from what was cooked or did you have to eat a bit of everything?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Yes, father'd say
, if you can't eat that for dinner, he'd say, he'd say, you're going to have it for tea, you won't have no more for tea. He said you aint hungry if you can't eat that. So I - what I didn't used to eat for dinner I had to eat for tea.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Did you by and large eat up what you'd got already?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Yes. Yes, I shouldn't get no other else.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Did you ever ask for a second helping?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Yes, if I wanted it I could have it. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Were you expected to hold your knife and fork in a certain way or sit in a certain way?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Well - hold 'em ordinary and - never nothing said about that, you had to sit up proper, to - to table.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 If there was something on the table, like the salt, could you ask for someone to pass it on or would you have to wait?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 I should - I should have to wait for it, ate what I got on plate.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 But say you wanted the salt?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Could you just ask for it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Yes. Say, please - pass over the salt please?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Could you bring toys or a book to the table?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 No. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 You weren't allowed to?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 You had to have - you was sat in the table then.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 When could you leave the table?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 When - when - oh when they've all finished.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 So nobody could leave the table before?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Oh no, you - you used to go - you wouldn't go away in they days.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Did all the family sit at the table?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Yes. Mother - well there was only me and father and mother home then.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 But you'd all sit when you were there together?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 And the lodger stopped there too when he was there.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Would he have tea with you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Yes, he - yes. He'd have his own food what he brought from his home.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Would he cook it himself?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 No, oh no, mother had to cook it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Would he eat with you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Yes. Certainly, yes, if he was there when I - had mine he'd eat with us.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 What about supper, did he have supper?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 No. No. Only when he cook - that's right, only when - only when he come home from his work.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Did you always have the same places at the table?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Oh no, we sit any place so long as you was down - sit down.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 How was the meal served, who would serve the meal?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Mother.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Would she bring it to the table?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Yes. Well put it all on the table and she'd take it out and put it on your plate and let you have it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 What order were you served in?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 What order?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Was your father served first?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Yes. Father first and me come last. Or mo - mother next and me - me next and mother last.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Would your mother always do the serving or would your father sometimes help? Would he ever do any carving?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 No, no, father didn't.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Can you remember what would ha-pen before you were old enough to feed yourself, would you sit at the table then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Oh I don't know. I can't remember that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Was your mother an easy person to talk to?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Yes, nice person, yes, quiet. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Did she show a lot of affection?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Yes.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 If you had any worries could you share them with her or not?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 No. Only father.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 You would share your worries with father rather than your mother?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Why was that do you think?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 I don't know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 What about your father, was he an easy person to talk to?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Yes, he's quiet. Little bit hard of hearing like I be.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 You say you took your worries to him, what kind of worries would you take to him?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Oh I never had no worries in they days, not that I can mind.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 How did your parents expect you to behave towards them?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Oh if I didn't do anything right I should get the stick. In they days, yes, father give me the stick many a time. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 What kind of things would you do wrong?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 
Oh I - that was answering back father. He give me the stick, he said - I were - if I was out you know doing anything wrong or that. You'd get the stick in they days.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Did you mind?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Who mind, me? Oh I had to - I had to mind didn't I.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Did your parents bring you up to behave towards your brothers and sisters in a certain way, that wouldn't apply?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 No, but they was - no, they was all gone out you see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Did they ever come back, your brother and sisters?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 
No, well only they come home perhaps when there was - when there was their half day out from service. See what I mean, they get half a day perhaps in they days for - for to come home for see their p
arents and - for - they was allowed certain hours see. That's all.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 You didn't really see an awful lot of them?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 No, no, no, no. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 What did your parents say about b}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12916761\charrsid9705256 ea}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 tting other children, say another child hit you would they say hit him back, what would be their attitude on that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Oh they never hurted me much like that. No. No. No. No, only make - as long as you done what was right they - they be all right.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 What kind of people do you think your parents hoped you'd grow up to be?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Good peo - brought me up to be good.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 What did good mean?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Well live so well as you can.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Did they bring you up to consider certain things important in life?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 No. No, I never - said nothing about that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 What did they think of swearing?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Oh we - never swear, I never sweared, father never sweared. No, never swear - that never worried us swearing.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Did they bring you up to be religious do you think?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Yes, 'cos I had to go - I had to go chapel three times every Sunday before I was old enough to leave.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 How old would that be when you left?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 When I - when I was about fourteen. That was when I left - for to go down to Bovey to - to - to live.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 You left home when you were fourteen?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Yes. I - I did up there, but I went - still went home when I was down Bovey. For a little while. And -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 To stay at home or to go to chapel? You say you left home when you were fourteen?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 You went back home again, what did you go home for, to live?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 No, I - I - I went to Southbrook to work with father for a little while.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 This was when you left home?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 That was when I left Oldertown. He went to Southbrook, and I worked up by with father on the farms for so long.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Where would your home be then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 At Southbrook.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 So you'd still be living at home?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 
Yes, Southbrook, yes. And when - and then we shifted houses from Southbrook and went in East Street in Bovey Tracey to live. And - and - that was about - I was about seventeen then. And I went to work - work for a road contractor - for two or three years.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 This is before you went back onto the farms again?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 That - that - this is after. You see, after I left Southbrook in I went in East Street at Bovey to live. I left father then. I use
d to come to sleep but I - I worked for another man. A stone cart.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 What did you do then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 
Driving a horse and cart. About two or three years. And then the war come. And I used to go about with a - a - the - ambulance in they days, that was 19 - 15, and then in 1916 - I went in the Army, went to France in 1916.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 What did you do when you came back from the war?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 From the war?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 What job did you do then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 I went to the - I worked in the stone quarry out at - at - Trosson.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Where's that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 That's about - three miles from Bovey towards Exeter way, Chunleigh.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 What were you doing in the quarry?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Ripping stone, and - with trolleys, loading up trolleys and pushing 'em. I was working for three years. Then - then I had - th
en there was forty of us sacked one morning.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 What was that for?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Sacked 'cos the - slack of orders. Getting no orders.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 What did you do then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Then I come out here and got married.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 In the Staveton area?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 That's right. About a fortnight after I got married I was out of work. Out of work for three months.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 What did you do when you came to live here, what did you do for a job?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 I - jobbing about didn't I, different jobs down on the river and - for Commissioners and that wasn't I.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 What kind of jobs would you be doing on the river?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Pieringor anything wasn't it. Hedging.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Have you done this all your life since then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 And - and then I - and then I worked for the - road contractors. I worked - three or four y
ears for they. And they all lost the contract and I went - and I got a job on the council. I started on the council in 1927. Under the Rural District Council. And I worked then for I was sixty-eight.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 So you've worked the best part of your life for the council?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 I've worked nearly all my life on the roads.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 When grown ups were talking were you allowed to join in can you remember?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Yes, in meals. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Any time during the day.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 You could do what you liked in the way of talking like that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Oh mustn't talk at table.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 But apart from that could you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Were you allowed to talk when grown ups were talking?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 You say that when you did something wrong your father would give you the stick?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Did your mother ever give you the stick for anything? Did your mother ever punish you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 No, no - no, only father. Mother would never - never - not she.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Can you remember any particular occasion when you were punished?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Yes, I re - I
 remember once when - I'd done something wrong, I weren't very old over Longston and I done something, I can't understand - mind what it is now but - I now mother chased me up the road and I - I could run faster than her and I stopped and laughed at her b
ecause her couldn't catch me, I can remember that. Of course, you have it when you come home, her said.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 And did you have it when you came home?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 I can't remember now.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Would you say you received the ideas on how to behave from both your parents or was one more important in that than the other?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Yes. Father was - fa - me father was the strictest. Stricter - stricter than mother.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Did you sort of look up to your father for guidance more than your mother?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 I used to be more afraid of him than I was of mother.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 But you liked your father even so?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Oh I like him all right, yes, he was all right to me, only he was strict.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 But you expected that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 I know I shouldn't have never say nothing back, 'cos see I should get it more if I done that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 When you had a birthday would it be different from any other day?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 No, just the same as ordinary day.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 You wouldn't get presents?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 No, not in they days.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Did you have anything special to eat on your birthday?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 No. Only thing I used to get was when us went chapel. Harvest - Sunday school. And only thing different in they days.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 What would you have then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Well - a - a treat.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 How often would you have a treat?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Once a year. That was at - owing to - that was belonging to the chapel Sunday school.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 What would you do on this day of the year? What would you do for your treat?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Well - you - used to get a - go - go - go chapel, you see, so many weeks then you was entitled to a - a treat once a year.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 What would this treat consist of?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Oh all the cake and - butter, brown bread.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Would you eat it at the chapel or would you bring it home?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 No, you had to sit on a great long table, both sides with children see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 It was just the children?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 That's right, only children.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 What time of year was this?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 I think it was in August.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Did you ever go any sort of trips to the seaside?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Oh weren't no trips in they day, nothing - nothing like that in they days. They couldn't afford it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Were you ever in the chapel choir?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Never in a choir. No. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Can you remember anything you did with your father and mother on Christmas Day?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Was Christmas Day the same as any other day?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 That's right.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Would your father work on Christmas Day?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Same as ordinary day, had to do his horses.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 So you didn't sort of have anything different at Christmas time really?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 No. Only thing different you may have a Christmas pudding. Well ordinary Christmas pudding, that's all.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 You wouldn't have something like fowl or something for Christmas dinner?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 You may have a fowl, you may have a bit of pork.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 But it wouldn't be a sort of a completely different day to the rest of the year?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 No, no, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Did you have any musical instruments in your home?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 No, no, no, nothing at all.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Was there anyone in the family who sang?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Did you ever make music together as a family at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 No. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Did your parents ever play any games with you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 No, not that - that I can mind. Unless I was small, I can't mind it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 What about books or newspapers, were there any books or newspapers?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Well - used to have - have Sunday school books. In they days, once a year.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 You'd get them as a prize would you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 As prizes, that's right.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 But you wouldn't have other books in the house?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 What about newspapers?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 I don't think it was like be today. I can't remember.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Magazines?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 No. But I - I - one paper, Western Times in they days.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Did your father or mother get that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Do you ever remember your mother or father reading?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Used to go - chapel - evening sometimes. Twice a week - about seven, eight o'clock in the night.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Not on Sundays?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 No. No, I'm speaking - in the week this is. Perhaps Tuesdays and Thursday night.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Would you go as well?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 I should have to go with father - and mother.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 You'd all three go out?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 That's right.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 What would you do at the chapel then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Well there - there - what they called prayer meetings in they days.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 What would they consist of?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Me father used to lead in prayer and that you see, he'd take it - one would get up and say a prayer and then another would -
 get up and say a prayer and used to go round the chapel. The men.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Did many people go to these prayer meetings?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Well when - when I used to go there used to be - the chapel used to be full every Sunday nearly - in they days. And us used to get ab
out a hundred, perhaps two hundred children of a Sunday.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Used to sing what?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 
Sing san - what they call Sankey hymns in they days, there's a book called Sankey. He - he was a Methodist. He was a Methodist, Sankey see. That's what they used to sing in they days, Sankey hymns.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 What kind of people went to the chapel?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Oh all different kinds of people, mostly working class and farmers.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Was there many churches in that area, it was in the country side wasn't it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Yes. There was a chur
ch there too but you know about a mile and a half away. But the chapel used to be full in they days, after - afternoons and evenings.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 It was a Methodist chapel was it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Methodist chapel.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 But you can't remember your mother and father reading anything else except the Bible?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 No. No. No, I can't mind 'em reading nothing but the Bible.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Did they ever read aloud to you or to each other?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 They'd read the Bible?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 That's right.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Every day?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Well I don't know about every day, I can't remember now.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Do you remember a funeral in the family at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Were you ever taken out visiting neighbours?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 No, only took out to - maybe took out for - for to see me oldest sister down at - South Knighton. Fat
her'd have a pony and trap in they days and take us down for the - few hours. That's all.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 How often would you go there?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Oh, about once in - twelve months perhaps.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 So you didn't really go out visiting an awful lot?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Didn't go very often, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 You say your brother and sisters only came back occasionally when it was half day or something?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 I suppose your brother being in the mines wouldn't get home hardly at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Would you ever go out to see neighbours?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 No, no, no, 'cos mother was never - never nothing visiting less her - same as when her used to go out - going chapel or - or that like.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Would you have many friends come back from chapel?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Yes, oh you'd have 'em at chapel but - all houses a l
ong way away from their neighbours. They was all in different - different - way you see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Would you ever go round visiting after chapel?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Oh no, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 You'd just come back home?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 That's right. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Were you ever taken out shopping?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Yes, used to go Bovey - when - with my mother shopping.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 When would you go there?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 And Saturdays as a rule.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Every Saturday?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Oh not every Saturday, only when I wanted clothes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Which was only about once ever few years?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 That's right.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Where would you get most of your food and things from, would the shopkeepers come to you rather than you go to the shopkeepers?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Oh - we used to grow our own vegetables but - and then the bread used to - the bakers and that used to come
 round, bakers and the - and the grocers and all that you know. I should - there used to be one shop in Usington.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 So by and large you wouldn't have to go very far to get your stuff?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Oh no, no. Only about two mile.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Most of it was delivered to you was it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 
Yes, yes, lot of it and I lot I used to go in the shop and get. When I went to school - go down after I come out of school and bring it home, what I wanted.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 So you did quite a lot of errands for your mother in those days?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Yes, used to take errands you see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Would you ever do any errands for anybody else?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 No. No. Only - only taking round milk like I said in the beginning.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Did you ever go out with just your father, you say you went in the horse and cart, the pony
 and trap to see your sister in South Knighton, would you ever go out with your father on any other occasions?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 I - no, only father and mother. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 You went out as a family usually?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 I went out to see me sister.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Can you remember any other outings with your parents at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 No, that's only - no, that's only place us went - with the horse and trap.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Did you have Bank Holidays in those days?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 No, I don't think - no, no, weren't no Bank Holidays in they days. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Did you ever go away for a holiday?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 
No. Never - never had a holiday in me life. Not in they days, no, they couldn't afford it. They only had about eleven, twelve shillings a day - or a week.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 That's your father's wage?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Did your father attend any clubs or pubs at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Yes, he was in - the - the Rational Club.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 What's that then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 
For paying - so much if he'm sick isn't it, what you get. If you'm home sick you can draw so much a week from the club you see, if you pay into the club. But that isn't very much, you pay - but you don't get out very much. Only helps some little bit.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Did he go to any social club activities?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 No. No, father never - I never knowed father have any of that. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 So he didn't go in for any social activities at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Did your father ever take part in any sport at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 No. Weren't none about in they days.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 What about horse racing?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 No, no, no, he's the last one would do that. That's the Devil's work he said. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 He didn't bet then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Did your father belong to any other clubs?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 No, only the Rational.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 He didn't belong to a boot club?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 No, no, no. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Or a funeral club?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 How did you get on with your brother and sisters, do you remember any contact with them after they'd moved away?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 
No, well they - they may come home and see mother for like I told you for hour or two of a day when - when it's their time off from service, that's all.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 How would they look upon you, would they tell you stories or anything like that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Oh I was - lot younger than all they you see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Would they sort of come home and tell you what the world was like outside?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 No.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 You don't remember anything like that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 No, no, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Who did you play with when you were a child?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 I used to have mates, down Trumpeton. Used to be happier in they days playing than they be now.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Would these be children you were at school with?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Children I used to go to school with. I used to interest meself a lot of the time.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Doing what?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 
And now they got to have different things for they can't be happy without they'd doing something for 'em. I had to make me own happiness in they days.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 What kind of things did you do?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 
Well - I used to go up and - plantations, looking out for squirrels and - picking up stones, aiming at 'em to see if I could knock 'em off and - yes, all different things.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 You went birds nesting did you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Did you ever collect things?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 No, no, no, I never collected none. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 What about things like flowers?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 No. No. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Did you do much gardening when you were still young?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Oh help - help father in the garden. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 I shouldn't think he had much time for gardening if he was out in the farm?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 No. Only - only - only in the sum - on - you know, in latter nights like.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Would your mother do any gardening?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Oh - oh no, no. No. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Did you have any pets at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 No, only cat. Yes. Had a cat.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Did you have any hobbies?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 
No. Never had no hobbies in they days. Oh I - yes, I used to keep tame pigeons. That's right, I used to keep they. Then - wasn't allowed to keep 'em though 'cos if policeman know it you'd get had up.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Why?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Whe
n - when I was young I used to go up top of a fir tree - when the wild pigeons was hatching, just when they was feathered, I'd take 'em home, climb down the tree and bring 'em home and put 'em indoors and rear 'em, they'd be lovely pigeons.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 So your tame pigeons were in fact wild pigeons?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 
Yes, that was wild pigeons they used to call 'em, they used to - used to - have tame pigeons too. One would go up fir tree, they - they - little flat nests, but they only lay two eggs. And I'd go up one day see '
em getting bigger and then - at last I'd bring 'em home, put 'em in a bag or something, come down the tree, and take 'em home and - and rear 'em. They'd get lovely pigeons. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 What did the policeman think, you say the policemen -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Well wasn't -
 wasn't much policeman about in they days, he - I used to keep the door shut when I - knowed he was about. But then they wasn't about then like - you know what I mean, wasn't the rogues about then like there is today.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 I thought you said the policeman?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Oh he'd have you if he - you wasn't allowed to keep wild ones but he couldn't say nought to you with - keeping tame ones. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Why weren't you allowed to keep wild ones? One of the laws of the country?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Yes. Yes. You aren't allowed to keep wild ones, not even like that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Whereabouts would you play when you were young?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 
Trompetor. There was some cottages down there I used to play with they. And they - they all had each - each one had certain amount of work to do before they could go out and play with they.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 What kind of jobs would they have to do?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 
They had to clean boots sort of and the maidens had to do other things before they could go out to play. They couldn't go out play first thing in the morning, they all had their w
ork to do. So I been down there a long time going out and - waiting for they finished their work before I could play with 'em.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Were you playing before going to school as well?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Oh, played with meself, that's all. But I couldn't play with they afo
re they'd done their work. And then they could come and play, they had certain amount of work to do of a - of a morning before they came out.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 You'd have a lot of work to do as well wouldn't you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Yes, I done - I used to do my work every morning, going round carrying milk.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 What time did you say you had breakfast, about eight o'clock or half past eight?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Me, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Would you get up much before that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 I had to get up before that, about quarter past seven.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 What time would your father have to get up?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 
I had to go down the farm, by - about four hundreds yards and fetch the milk. Bring it home, go have a - have across one or two fields to take it up this gentleman's house and I used to come home, mother had a lovely fried break
fast ready for me when I got home, fried bacon and eggs and oh and lovely - potatoes, you know, sliced as then - as they grow you know, sliced, beautiful it was, yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 What time would your father have to get up in the morning?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Oh he'd get up
 afore that, he's gone work - he could go - he had to be down his work half past six, it was half past six in they days. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Were you free to play with anybody you pleased?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Yes, I used to play the handiest to me. Or any of 'em that used to go to school was all right.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 There was nobody your parents said to keep away from?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 No, no, no, no. I know us used to fight sometimes - in they days, you know, boys like.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 What would the teachers think if you went fighting? Or would this be outside the school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Well that - you forget all about that. Used to play marbles in they days.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Our side or inside school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Were you allowed to get dirty when you played?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Well but - mother didn't make all - didn't use - make much odds like that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 How often would she have to do the washing, once a week?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 What, mother? I expect so.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Was it all countryside around where you were living?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Yes? All country.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 There wasn't much town or many streets and things?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 There wasn't no streets, all country. Narrow roads.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Would you ever play in other boys or other girls homes at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Yes. That's why I used to go down with they to play, down in their homes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 You'd play inside rather than outside?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 No, no, play outside. Where they had their homes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Would you ever do anything inside the house?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 No, no, no, they wouldn't let you do that. No, you'd get the stick if you did go in their - bring in your mud in there. That wouldn't do.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 I wondered if you had indoor games like cards or something like that to play?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Chasing around here and all that us used to be in they day.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Were you very naughty as children, did you get in peoples way at all? When you were children did you get in the grown up's way at all?

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 No. No. No. I can't remember that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Did you ever go fishing at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Fishing, no. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 How about walking, did you ever go for walks at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Bicycling, did you have a bicycle?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Did you ever take part in any sports?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12916761\charrsid9705256 You didn't play football or an}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 ything like that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 No, no, wasn't about then.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Did you go to any theatres?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 No. Weren't nothing.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Concerts?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 No, I used to go hunting. Hunting. Hunting foxes. Hunting.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 What would you do then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 
We - used to go up - Moorland Hotel, every Ch - Boxing Day. You see - the hounds used to meet there, and everybody, they used to give beer and chee}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12916761\charrsid9705256 se}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256  - bread and cheese for - a meal, in they day. That was Boxing Day.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Would you actually take part in the hunt?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Well you - you keep on walking like that where they was hunting see, see what you could see.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 You don't remember any sort of organised entertainments like theatres and cinemas?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 No. No. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Did they ever have any sort of village concerts?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 No. No, wouldn't be nothing like that then. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Do you remember anything like a fair or a circus?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 No. Nothing - nothing like that then..
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Did your parents ever give you any pocket money?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Any?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Any pocket money?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 No, only - no. Well I used to - well I used to and father - mother used to help keep the home going then.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 This is when you were earning money?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Yes. Well that - that used to go towards the home.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Did you get paid for doing the milk round?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Oh yes, of course I did - I used to get so much a week, not very much though. About nine}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid12916761\charrsid9705256  }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 pence or a shilling a week.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Who'd pay you that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 The - no, the - the - the gentleman. The gentleman who I took it to.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Where would you get your milk from to take up there, the farm?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Yes, the farm wouldn't pay me, the - the - where I took the milk, the lady would pay me for carrying it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Would you have to pay the farmer for the milk in the first place?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 
I should have to take a bill up to 'em, and they'd let me have the money perhaps and I had to pay - take it down to the farmer. See what I mean?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 And you'd get something for doing the errands in between?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Yes, well I shouldn't get it from the farmer, I should get it from - the gentleman.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Did you get any money for helping with the moles and the rabbits?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 No. No, I used to do that for father. Used to go round all the gins perhaps of a morning. Take 'em out and - you'd hear the gins ratt
ling.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 What would you do with them then, you'd just bring them back to the farm or the cottage?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 No, take 'em home to - home to - home to father.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Were you ever given lessons by one of your parents?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Or a tutor or a governess? How old were you when you first we-t to school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 When I went school? Five year old.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 What time in the morning did you go?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 When I used to live over Longston oh - oh I'd be in school be nine o'clock.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 How far away was school from the cottage?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 About two miles.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 How long would that take?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 
Well twenty minutes, all depends whether - when the bell was ringing. If the bell was ringing I should run faster, 'cos I know - 'cos I know I should get the stick if I wasn't there when the bell finished.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Would you get the stick for that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Cor yes, they used to in they days.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Did you get the stick very often?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Oh I - I didn't used to if I could help it. I used to be there by time the bell finished if I could save getting the stick.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 How many people went to this school?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Oh, hundred and fifty, two hundred perhaps.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 What kind of school was it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Oh ordinary school, church school.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 It was a church school rather than a board school was it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 No, it was the - just across - go across the road in the churchyard you was in the church.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 So it was opposite the church really?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Yes. Close to the church.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 What time of day would you go home?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Come out of school four o'clock.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 So from five years 
on you went to get there at nine o'clock and came home again after four o'clock? Did they carry on right through 'til you were fourteen?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Yes, that - thirteen. Yes. That's right.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 So you didn't sort of not go to afternoon school to begin with, you went to afternoon school and morning school straight away?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 All the - that's right, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Did you walk to school every day?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Yes, every day, rain or shine.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Would you walk on your own or did someone go with you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Oh I - I walked - I
 had to walk so far on me own 'cos there wasn't no other houses. And then when I got in - another house, there'd be several there be going to school now and then if they wasn't gone I should go on with they. But if they was gone I had to go with meself.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 But I suppose by and large you had a routine?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Meet the same people very day?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Yes - if us could, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 You say you'd have your midday meal at school? You'd take a pasty or something to school with you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Yes, that's right. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Would your mother make pasties?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 That - that's right. Lovely pasties, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 She was a good cook was she?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 That's right. Mother used to make they. And I'd take cold tea then, there wasn't no hot tea then they days. Used to take a med
icine bottle, mother'd fill it up with cold tea. And you had to drink that, that would last you all the day, weren't like no hot milk in they days like they get now.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 You wouldn't have school milk or anything like that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Oh no, never - nothing like that. Not in they days.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 What did you think of school, did you like school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 I - wasn't bad, well I mean sometimes I didn't like it, specially when if you had to keep on - keep on getting the stick.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Did you get the stick very often?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Y
es, I - oh especially when I - I know once when I done a sum - I'd done a sum once and the schoolmaster was strict. He said to me, he said, you've done this one before haven't you Radford? I said, no sir. He looked back over the pages, he see'd I - he see
'd I'd done it two days before, didn't he give me the stick. Oh didn't he make me hoot.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Did you have a different teacher for every subject?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Mm?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Did you have a different teacher for every subject, or was it one teacher per class?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 No, had different subjects. Sums - and - arithmetic, he'd given me it more than once. He'd give it -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Would the same teacher teach you all the subjects?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Yes, same one - he - he was called Mr Bonnup. The schoolmaster, he - he was very strict, but he - 
he didn't hurt ee. Now today they aren't strict enough. And you wouldn't do - we used to hold the pen in they days, if have your head over like this. If he come round with a cane he see'd you wasn't holding it properly, you - he - you - your knuckles woul
d be black after he rapped that - you know, the - the cane across 'em - in they days.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Did any of the children object to him or tell their parents about it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 No. I know - years before I went to school my mother - well - well used to show them so ba
d in they days that they used to black mark 'em and I - and her used to take the hold of me, my sisters and that to the - schoolmaster when he'd been there and show him up for - the black marks he used to put on 'em when they used to go school. If they - 
you know, where they was wrong, yes. He'd make black marks on me some of 'em would they schoolmasters, 'cos they'd - too much of that way then. But now they'm - other way about.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Did you have the same teacher?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Yes. All - yes, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Did you - he look after a hundred and fifty of you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 
No, no, he had - he had a - a - his wife used to teach the girls in sewing and all that and - and he used to have another - under he and he was the boss. Schoolmaster.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 But you had him all the time?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Was his wife like that as well?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 His - no, no, didn't used to teach me, his wife, only the girls. Young girls.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Did you hear any stores about what she was like?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 No. I don't know nothing about her. 'Cos her used to take just baby girls.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Did the boys and girls get separate lessons in this school then? Were they taught separately?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 No, us used to sit together. Boys and girls in they days. When you got older.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Would you ever do anything like geography or history?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Ye
s, geography, history, composition. You know - our schoolmaster would read out a paragraph or something on you know, and - read it, you had to mind what he read out. Of course I could - when he got half way through the composition I could mind that. When 
h
e got other - other half I - I could just - manage to rad the - mind the - where he said the meadow, I was - I was never - I could ne - so I - there used to be a maid who used to be a good scholar, and I used to copy from her. You know, I - and he caught 
me one day looking on her - cor didn't he give me the stick, and he shifted me from there, he put somewhere else, that was gone then and I didn't know what to do.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Did you ever have a special treatment, like a dunces cap for anything like that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 No. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 They didn't make you stand in front of the class?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 
No - no, what the used to do, he used to take us on his knee, and have a little short stick - and someone would - he couldn't take some boys on his knee 'cos they was bigger than he. I've s
een 'em - I've seen us stood behind laughing at 'em, well we didn't let he hear us laughing. The - the boys were bigger than he and - and they'd be rolling one after the other on the - on the - on the floor. And some of 'em he was afraid of.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Did anyone try and hit him back for being cruel?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 No, no. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 
What did you think about him hitting you with a stick and things, did you think he was a cruel man or did you think this was just part of at school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 No, it - well he was on the right, I m
ean to say he done us good by being strict, you know what I mean, you got to be strict with anything, you got to discipline with anything today. That's what the - the country's lost in discipline today. You see there's more discipline in they days than th
ere is now.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 You think he taught you things like punctuality?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 
Yes, you had to be there if they bell finished and you wanst there you was in for it. He'd see you go in behind the desk, whacking the old stick up and down you know. You know what used
 to happen. And some of 'em he'd say, put your hand out, and some would be take - whip - just as he was going that down they'd whip their hand back and then waited on the other one.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 What about tidiness, would he expect you to be tidy?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Yes, you had to be tidy. Yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Would he give you the stick if you were untidy?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 
Well I don't know about give you the stick, he'd tell you once but true he wouldn't tell ee again, probably give you the stick then perhaps.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 What about manners, did he expect you to be well mannered?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Oh yes, yes, you used to have to mind your manners in they days. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Did you think the teachers taught you to be well mannered?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Yes, used to teach you that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 What about speaking properly, did he say you'd got to speak properly, did he teach you things like that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Or did he expect things like that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 No. Us used to have the inspector come sometime.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 What kind of inspectors were these?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Scriptures inspector - scrip - scripture you know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 What would they do?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Oh - ask ee whether - questions about the Bible and that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Would you have any inspectors for anything else?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Would the teacher punish the girls the same as the boys? Would the girls get the same punishment, would they get the stick as well?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Yes. No, I don't think - he didn't use the - they like he did the boys.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 What would he do for the girls?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 No, he - they would stand at one side.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 In front of the class?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Yes. Perhaps make 'em stop in after - others gone home.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Can you remember any boys in your school or girls in your school who were always on their own, that nobody else played with them?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 No. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Everyone sort of joined in?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Always - mixed with mates in they days.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Did your parents show any interest in your school work?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 School work. Not that I know of, only - you see that I - I had to go everyday. They'd see that I went every day.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 What would happen if you didn't go?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Well father want -
 I never been like that, me own self would - 'cos I knowed if I didn't go I should get the stick from the schoolmaster, he'd want to know why I wasn't there.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Did your parents ever ask you what you did at school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Did they ever visit the school at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 No, not whilst I was at school.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Did they ever meet the teachers?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 No, and they - when they've been out for a walk or anything - meet the teachers.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Where did the other children live, what kind of homes did they live in?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Oh - cottages like - like us.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Was it mainly farming people round there?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Yes, farm and agricultural place.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 There wasn't any industry?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 There wasn't no in - wasn't no industry there.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 You say there were one or two people like this parson who was moving in from Torqyay? It was mainly sort of scattered settlements was it?

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Yes. Scattered, one or two here and one there.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Do you remember the teachers ever singling out children for different treatment from others? Did they have any favourites for instance?

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 No. No. What tables when us went school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 When you were in the class room did the teacher ever have anybody he particularly like or disliked?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 No, no, no, no. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 He treated you all the same?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Were there any gangs or groups in your school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 There wasn't sort of one end of the village against the next, the other end?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 That's all - always one.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 All one group?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 That's right.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 How old were you when you left school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Thirteen and a half.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Did you go on to any other school after?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 No, I didn't have the money to do it then.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Would you have stayed on longer if you'd have had the opportunity do you think?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 I should have if - had the opportunity like they got today. 'Cos I was well up in sums. I liked sums, I was the - I was in exp}{
\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12916761\charrsid9705256  }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 seven when I left.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 What's that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Well - the - the next up from seven only you can't go no higher without you go somewhere else. You know what I mean, well they
 go somewhere else today don't 'em. I couldn't go no higher then 'cos there weren't - weren't no - higher about. You see, if your parents didn't have the help like they got today, from the Government and all that for to - help people to go on high - other
 school, 'cos - weren't nothing like that then.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Did any of the other children in the school go on to another school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 No. No. No. No. None.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Did you ever go to any part time evening classes afterwards?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 No. No. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Did you ever have any regrets about your education?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 You think it did you a lot of good?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Yes, my - my - schooldays did, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 In what sense did they do you some good do you think?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Well - like arithmetic and - adding up now, well I can do now the sums and that. That's what I - I used to be - well even geography.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Did it ever make you want to travel around?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 When you were at school did they sort of concentrate on teaching you to read and write? Or did they do that one time of th
e day and then another time they do something else?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Would each day have different subjects in it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Yes, in the school. Oh it wouldn't be the same every day. You'd have different things every day.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Did you ever do any part time work while you were still at school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 No. Only - only -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 You say helped with the milk?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 That's right, in the morning.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 You didn't have a sort of a regular part time job on the side?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Oh no, no, that was - no, that was - I done it every day mind. That's all. That's all, carrying milk.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 What was your first job?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 I was -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Your first job you say was with your father when you moved?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Yes, that's right. From a farm up Smoller - up Oldertown. Yes. I worked with me father.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Did you work in Oldertown to begin with?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 That's right. For the first year or two.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Did you work on the same farm as your father?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Yes. Down Southbrook.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Where did you first start full time work, was it at Oldertown or was it at Southbrook?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Well - with me father. Down - yes, the Southbrook, Bovey Tracey.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 What would you do then, how many hours a day would you work?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Well from the - seven to five..
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 What would you do?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Anything on the go. Bending wood, hoeing turnips. Burning thorns. Hedging. All different sort - of things.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Would you do the same as your father and you wouldn't come home for breakfast?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 No, you take - you take that with you in the field. Sit down in the field by the hedge and have that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Did you ever have any sort of days when there was nothing much to do?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 No. Only this - only if it's raining, you couldn't go to work if it was raining.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 What would you do then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Oh stop home with mother.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Would your father do the same?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 You wouldn't get paid for it in they days. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Would your father stay at home?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Father wouldn't get paid if he stopped home. He'd have - h}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12916761\charrsid9705256 e}{\rtlch\fcs1 
\af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 'd have to make that up or try to, he was piecework. Make up for rainy day.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 How often would it rain?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Oh well - like do now I mean, never - you never know do see? Like do now, on and off like.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 So it was quite a sort of a risky business really?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Yes, yes, it was yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Was there any period of time when your father would be out of work for quite a long time?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 
Yes, well when we get - get no help you'd have to put up with that. You couldn't go - you wouldn't get no help from the parish or nothing, you had to make up that when it's dry weather. Work longer for to help make it up, you 
wouldn't get no help from nobody else in they days.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 What did the farmer say, did he sort of help you out at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 The farmer wouldn't help you out.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Did you get on with the farmers OK, did they find they were all much of a much or did you fin
d that one was nicer than another, a better boss than another?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 No, they didn't never worry 'cos then you'd knowed your job and - and when the job's finished there - there's your money.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Did you ever have any sort of social activities with the farmers families?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 No, no, no. No. No, only work - only working with 'em. Working for 'em I mean. That's all.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 How many farm labourers were there working on the farm, the one in Southbrook where you first started?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Well, all depends, perhaps two or three, four in they days.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Would you live next door to each other?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 No, no, they live apart, long ways apart from one another.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Was the place in Southbrook very far from where you lived, the farm?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Well some - some would be further than others you see. You had to go where the work was, don't matter is a long way or a short way.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Why do you think you made all these different changes of house, was that because your father had to go out and find a new place to work?

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 No. My fath
er - why us left Oldertown - 'cos the farmer weren't very good, he - he weren't much very cop. And - and - and father left there and went to - went to Southbrook, and father thought to himself well he ain't keeping my boy behind, he'll treat ee like a dog
. So father, when he left he said he was taking me and I went with father then. Before I got older.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Where was your mother, did she move with you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Yes, of course her did, her moved from the - from - Oldertown to Southbrook, wouldn't leave mother b
ehind. 'Cos that's three mile away. And I - I worked with father then for several years. Before I was got older and I thought to myself well I want to get me own wages. And I went and worked for a - a stone carter, driving a stone cart for two or three ye
ar.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Was this before the first world war or just after?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 
That was before the first - first world war, I worked for ee - for three years. Yes. At Bovey Tracey. And I had a job - he wanted a man driving a stone cart. So I worked for ee. And the Army wanted men, I went with \{BLANK\}
 then in they days for twelve months, and at last I was called up. And I went in the Army. Fortnight. In the Fourth Devons. I was on parade one day and they wanted men in the \{BLANK\} machine guns. I was picked out with a lot 
of other men to go in the fitters machine guns, I would come home on leave first. And then I went back in and done me training with 'em on Lincolnshire, and in six weeks I was across to \{BLANK\}
 on the Somme. That was in 1916. And nearly blowed sky big first night on the Somme.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 So you did about six years work before you went in the first world war?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 You did about three years farm work, and about three years for the stone quarry?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Yes. Yes, that's about it, yes, yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Which did you prefer of the two? Farm working or stone cart?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Well - I - farm works all right but if I had my days to go over again I'd work on the roads.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Was it more security?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Well it isn't only that, it's out in the fresh air too. And - and - a
nd farmers weren't nice to work for in they days, they're different now. 'Cos they can't have all their say in these days like they used to then. See?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Did you find by and large farmers were quite unfriendly towards you? Did they expect you to work a lot for not much money?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 
Yes, more than they do now. 'Course you couldn't say nothing in they days, but now the - the boots on the other foot. See, they're no boss now.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Did your father ever complain about farmers?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 No, no, he used to pay him his wages while he worked for him.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 I mean when he was at home?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 
No. He was happy enough. Of course he had to be in they days 'cos there wasn't the work about. You couldn't say nothing in they days, proper Tory days then.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 You say you worked from seven o'clock in the morning 'til five o'clock at night on the farm job?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Yes.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Did you work every day of the week or was that just Monday to Friday?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Every day of the week.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 What about Saturdays and Sunday?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Oh Sundays - I woul
dn't work Sundays, only - not - Saturdays afternoons for four o'clock. That's right, Saturday, you wouldn't work Sundays.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Did you have any half days?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 No, only - after four o'clock.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Did you ever have any holidays with pay?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 No. No. Nothing like that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 What were you paid in those days?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Eighteen shillings a week.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 What was your father's wage?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Father had - father'd get about - about - twenty-two or twenty-four perhaps, all depends what he hold if he -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 So there wasn't much difference between what you were getting and what he was getting
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 
Only fine - it was piecework father, you see, the more he done more he get - it isn't like mine, mine was a week's wages you see, eighteen shillings a week for driving a horse and cart.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 But your father was on piecework was he?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 He - he - father didn't work with me, I was - me father used to work on a farm piecework, I - I didn't used to know what he earned.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 You got the job in Southbrook to begin with because of him?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 
Yes, well I had to give - when I was working with my father I didn't used to get no wages, father - that used to come to - father - father used to have that you see. I didn't get no wages when I was with father. 'Cos that helped when - when - went t
owards the home.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 What period are we talking about now, are we talking about the period when you left school at thirteen?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 From thirteen to sixteen?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 That's right.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 When you were working for your father?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Yes, yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 You didn't get any money then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 No, no, no, 'cos I - mine and father's all reckoned as one.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 The farmer would pay your father for both of you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 That's - father used to get - go for the wages, he used to get it. That was - mine was in with 
his and I didn't used to get no wages. Used to go towards help paying me - for me food and that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 So the money would go to your mother indirectly?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 That - that's right.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 It would be spent on your board and keep?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Yes. That's right.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Did you have any lodgers to look after when you went to Southbrook?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 No, no, none at all, only me, father and mother.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 How did you get on with the other people you worked with?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 All right. Yes. Not - it's all right working with 'em.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 When you became a stone carter how did you find that? Did you find that was a completely different way of life to being on a farm?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Oh I got used to it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Did you work with many people?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 I worked with - used to be four men worked there, on the sam
e job as me when I went on me own. You know, driving the stone cart. Used to be four men, you was different - have a horse each like. Four horses a cart that's all on this little farm. Or - contractor I mean. He used to contract for the roads - in they da
ys. See you had to go to the quarry and get the stone and trail beside the hedges, and then there would be people to break 'em up in heaps, perhaps you've never seen 'em, they break 'em up in heaps beside the hedge in they days.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Would you take it to the road or would somebody else shift it to the road?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 
I should - no, I should - after I took 'em to they'd take 'em out big first, you'd put 'em big beside the hedge and then you'd have a road cracker come on with a hammer, and he'd crack 'em up - so s
mall, and then after a time - when the roller come along, you had to go with your horse and cart, and help load they with other men in your - cart for to take in front of the roller to roll in.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 It was only a very small concern you say, only four of you plus the contractor?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 It wasn't a very big man. He had a - his farm about twenty or thirty acres perhaps, only he used to do work for the council you see.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 So he was a farmer himself?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 He - yes, but he didn't used to do nothing. He didn't used to do nothing, he was too fat.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 He used to just live on a farm?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 That's right, he used to have - he used to like go down and have a pint in the night.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 How did you get on with him, was he OK as an employer?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Oh I - for - yes. First day I started little narrow - little old narrow up}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid12916761\charrsid9705256 -}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 
way to come out through the houses you know, just room enough for the cart. Oh I - of course I didn't think a lot about it, I hop on - jump up on the shafts and ride - here, he said, you get off, it isn't - 
it isn't - you mustn't ride out here he said, walk out.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Was he strict?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 He was - oh he - funny old card he was, yes. Yes. I thought to myself, I'm - I'm off from you as soon as I get the chance. I did too.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Did he pay you well or what?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 
Oh eight - eighteen shillings a - oh he was all right for your wages. You get that once a week, he come round with it. And - and you was out in the stable, well it was a fair wage I suppose in they days, eighteen shillings a week see. That's all they used
 to get for horse and carting, men, in they days, twelve shillings a day.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Did you find him better to get on with than say the farmers?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Oh I got on all right with him - less I see'd of him the better I mean.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 What kind of hours would you work on that, it was seven to five at the farm job?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 What about this job?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Us used to start seven o'clock 'til five I think. Yes. And - and Saturdays four four o'clock.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 So it was roughly the same hours as it was on the farm?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Yes. That's right. Then I left there and - I told you - oh I went in the Army that's right.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 When you came out of the Army?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Yes, he thought he was going to get me back but I - didn't go back with ee again, I got a job out Trussen quarry. I didn't use
d to forget who used to treat me when I was working for him see. He was wicked with my father 'cos I didn't come back with him again. But I didn't go back with him, I went to Trussen quarry.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Your father meanwhile was still working on this farm?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Father - father was still working about on firms himself, not - not on this farm but other farms he was. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 What did farmers think if a farm labourer moved around? Was that the normal procedure in those days?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Well - oh they didn't make no odds
 with it because - because it was about in they day. Because some farmers couldn't afford to keep a man all the time. See? And then - like father would go so many days a week perhaps, a day a week or do a h}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid12916761\charrsid9705256 e}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 dge or anything like that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 When you left Sou
thbrook farm to go into work for this stone carter did your father stay on at that farm very much longer or did he leave there again?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 No, he work - he worked on - keep on working about different places.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 But did you live at home still?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 I lived at home still, yes. Yes, 'cos I wasn't married see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Did you live at home until you got married?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Yes, lived with mother.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 When you came out of the army in 1918 how long did you do this job at Trussen?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 In the quarries? Oh I expect about two or three years. Couple years perhaps.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 What were you doing in that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 That closed down.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 You said forty of you were laid off?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 And I was laid off for three months, I had to go on the dole, forty of us. And I had a job - I come out
 here and got married - and I used to work about anywhere where I could get a job you know, doing anything - for the time. But then I knowed the road - road contractor what wanted a man, I went down - Combe. And worked for the contractors down there. I wo
rked for one contractor three year, and the other - couple of years. And they lost the contract, and I went in and - and said - surveyor in Totnes and got a job on the roads, 1927. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 So there was a gap of about six years when you were doing odd jobs here and there around this area?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 You didn't have sort of fixed job as such?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 No. No, that - that - I didn't start that afore 1927. I had one constant employer then before I retired.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Was it Staveton or Totnes council?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Totnes - Totnes District.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Would you ever have preferred another type of occupation do you think?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 No. No, I was happy enough on the same job. Yes. I was happy enough.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Did you ever serve an apprenticeship or a training period?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 No, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Did you ever belong to any trade union?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 What trade union?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 N - NPU - National Union of Public Employees. That's the council one.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 When did you join that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Oh -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 After the first world war?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Oh I - I hadn't been it more than - about - four or five years afore I retire - retired I expect.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Were there any trade unions before the first world war for farm workers?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 No, no, I don't think there was. I don't think there was. I wasn't in it anyway.}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid12916761\charrsid9705256  I only been in it recently. I }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 ain}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12916761\charrsid9705256 \rquote }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 t in it now.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 So you wouldn't take part in any trade union activities before the first world war?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Did you find that employers and workers had the same interest in those days before the first world war? Did you ever think about it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 They - they had more interest in the work - before the war than they have today.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 
But do you think they had similar outlooks? Did you think the employers and the workers were the same, or were they different types of people?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 No, they 
- they - they used to work together different in - in olden days - than they do now, the master and man. Used to be more friendly to one another.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 So you didn't have any real trouble with farmers?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 No, not in they days. No, not much in they days.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 
Did you ever have much contact with the farmer or this chap who was the contractor outside of work, would you see him socially outside of work?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 No. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Some people say in those days that there was a great division between trained craftsmen and other workers, did you find anything of that?

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Did you come into much contact with trained craftsmen?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Did you ever think there were any divisions of interest amongst workers?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Any interest in 'em?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Division of int
erest, did you think one group of workers would think themselves better than others? Or that they had more responsibility than others?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Yes, well - they knowed their responsibility then. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Do you think full time work changed your general attitude to life in any way?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 No, I don't think so.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 You'd been trained into getting up early and hard work from a very early age?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 You say when you were still at school that your father wouldn't get in 'til Saturday teatime, you wouldn'
t be at school on a Saturday would you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 How would you spend Saturdays?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Well - play after I done me work.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 What kind of things would you play, just amuse yourself really?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Yes, well - like I said, go down the - go down in the c
opse. Chasing squirrels and - anything, roaming about or - amuse myself different things by meself or I used to go down and see - the other school mates.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 How about Sundays, you say you went to chapel three times, did you go to Sunday school as well?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 
Yes, went Sunday school eleven o'clock in the morning. Come home. Have me dinner. And be in Sun - be in chapel again with father and mother, three o'clock in the afternoon. Come home again, have tea, be in again by six o'clock or half past. Chapel. T
hree times every Sunday.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 So the first would be Sunday school and the second two would be services?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Yes, the first - eleven o'clock Sunday school.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Did your parents go?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Not - yes - they had to go - me - I went with me parents in the aft
ernoon and evening. And I went in meself in the morning, to Sunday school, only for children.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Did your parents think it was wrong to work or to play on Sunday?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Play 'em?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 To work or play on Sunday, did your parents think it was wrong?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Yes, they went in the - afternoon and evenings.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 But did they think it was wrong?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 
No, I had to go then in they days, there's - it's right for me to go. They used to go in they days. Parents and - nearly everyone used to go chapel or church in they days. When I was young.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 What would they think of things like playing on Sundays?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 
Oh they - they would - they wouldn't do like they do today. They wouldn't play cricket and football like they do today, not in they days. They think it was wicked.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 So they disapproved of working and playing on Sundays?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 They disapproved of that - of doing that of a Sunday in they days.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 You say there weren't any Sunday school outings that you can remember, just this Sunday school treat once a year?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Yes, that's right, Sunday school tea, or - you know, a treat.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 You mentioned the prayer evenings?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Were there any other social activities organised by the chapel?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 No, nothing but the chapel.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Did the chapel organise anything else?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 No, no, no, no. No. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Did they run a temperance club?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 
Temperance? Well there's temperance in they days but of course - I don't think father belonged to that 'cos - I mean to say they - they used to like their cider in they days. 
See what I mean? They couldn't sign - sign the pledge very well when - and drink cider the same time.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Were you taught to say prayers at night?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Yes, when I - when I was a little - when I wasn't very old. When I used to go to bed mother used to pu
t me to bed, had to say your prayers every night.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Did you ever have family prayers all together?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 No. No, I can't remember that, 'cos they was - they was all gone before I got - can remember. See, they was a lot older than me.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Did your father ever take an interest in politics do you remember?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 
No, father never worried about politics. Only - what mother used to say, her said - the Tories got all the money, her used to say, they got all the say because they got the money, that's what my mo
ther used to say. That's all they used to worry about Tories then, we used to be Liberals in they days. Weren't no Labour then in they days.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Do you think your mother took any interest in politics other than that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Who?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Do you think your mother was very interested?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 
Me mother. Yes - yes, well that was - no, that was all used to say - I don't know whether was interested no always used to say father - the Tories got the money and they got - and - and - us can't do no about it. And they did 
have the money in they days Tories too.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Do you ever remember your father or your mother talking about it round the dinner table?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 No, up at - no, no, no, they never talk about that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Do you remember your father voting in a general election before 1918?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 No, I can't remember. It's gone.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 
So you don't know what party he voted for? In some places at that time men felt they risked losing their job or their house if they voted differently from their employers. Do you know if your father felt himself under that kind of pressure?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 
Now I know - no, but - they would if they could, but they didn't know who you voted for when you went down there behind the thing. But then - they - some of 'em was - we'd vote for Maister then in they days, '
cos they was afraid they'd get the sack. Father wasn't like that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 He wasn't told who to vote for?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Oh no. No. No. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 What do you think he would have done if he was told to?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 No, he'd please himself.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Your parents didn't take part in any political activity other than at a general election?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 No, no, nothing to do with that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Your father wasn't a member of any political party?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 No. Only the - member of the chapel, that's all.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Your mother wasn't either?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 What would your parents do when they weren't working?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 What did they do? Well he was always working about something. In his garden or that. There wasn't no outings or nothing in they days.

\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Did your mother have any interests outside of the house?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 She wouldn't go out to enjoy herself?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 There weren't any sort of women\rquote s institutes or mothers unions or anything like that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 No, no, no. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Did you ever have people round, you lived in about five houses before 191
8, in ever case was it sort of isolated, next to a farm in the middle of nowhere? Were you always sort of cut off from the community?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Yes. No, well us never see day without they pass the door.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 How did your father get home from work in the evenings?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Oh he walked.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 When did your father get home from work in the evenings?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Oh - he got home about - half past six perhaps. About six, seven o'clock.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 How many evenings a week would he spend at home, would he be in every night?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 He
 wouldn't go out again after he come home. Without - I used to go out and - with father - killing rabbit traps. He'd go out with killing rabbit traps if it's a nice night, perhaps he'd kill about thirty or forty gins. Dark night. And I had to go out and h
o
ld the lantern to him. He - he - he'd have a hut you know in a little seive, and sift it. I had to mind when I was up the - of course I've trodden right I suppose, he said, Jack, he said, could you see that tiller on that gun? I said, no father, I can't s
e
e. Well how do you expect for me to see it if you can't see it? Oh father said that to me many a time. He couldn't see what he's about if the light wasn't shining see, asked me whether I could see, no, I can't see it father, well how do you expect me to s
ee it then if you can't.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Did anyone outside the home ever help your mother look after the house or family?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 No.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 You don't remember any relatives coming round?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 No, they - all the relatives lived away up Exeter way, all our relatives. Ye
s, long - long way in they days. You couldn't see 'em then, you didn't have travel - or cars and that, couldn't go about see one another then in they days like they do today.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Did they come from a big family?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Yes. Big - yes, my - mother really ha
d nine and her lost three. Her had nine children really see, only they died just after they was born or something. I don't know a lot about it and -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 I don't mean your mother, I mean your mother?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Yes, they - the - the grannies and that had big fa
milies in they days. They all had big families in they days, my mother - mother's people and father's people lived while they was over ninety, in they days.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 What kind of things did they do, did they work on farms as well?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 No, I didn't - I never knowed, I never visited 'em.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 So you never saw your grandparents?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 No, I didn't know what they - no, 'cos us couldn't see one another often enough.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 You never had sort of cousins coming in occasionally?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 No, I don't know nothing about 'em - what they're doing.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Would your parents ever have friends come round in the evening?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 
Did they have anybody in the evenings? No, 'cos there weren't nobody round there, me father never used to go out after he come home, without I went out with him.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 So you'd only ever see people at the chapel say?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 No, not without was - not without he went to chapel that's all, went to the chapel night he see the chapel people then. That's all.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 But they never came back after chapel?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Oh no, they never come - up that way. We used to speak to - speak to 'em outside the chapel.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 But you wouldn't go out visiting other people?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Oh no, no, my - my mother never go visiting 'em. No, it wasn't like it be lot of 'em today.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 If your mother was ill, do you ever remember your mother being ill, or confined to bed, how did she manage?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 
No, I can't remember mother being ill. I know father had to go - go long way on a horse and back for fetch a doctor all down Bovey Tracey. I can't remember mother being ill. Her may have been but I can't - I can't go back.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Why did your father go off for the doctor?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 
Well he - he - he had to if any - anything bad or anything, he had to go down - ride from - from Oldertown to Bovey Tracey, have the doctor for anybody.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Did anything like that ever happen?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Yes, if anybody was bad well you see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Somebody in the neighbourhood?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Would he be the one that always went off to get help or would somebody else go sometimes?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Yes, well they come and father had a horse down see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Whose horse would this be, would it be the farmer's horse?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Yes, farmer's horse.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Did your parents have many friends do you think?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Had many friends? Yes - oh they had - nobody never disliked 
'em, not - not that I know of. They was all good neighbours in they days, they weren't jealous of one another like it be now.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Where did they see their friends?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Where to 'em come from?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Where did they see their friends?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Well - he seen his friends when he went to chapel or - and - different houses all along the different - houses he see 'em perhaps.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 What about the other farm workers, would they ever come back with your father, or would they go off in another direction after work?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 
Well he never see 'em after he'd left - after he'd been working with 'em all day. And sometimes you wouldn't see 'em 'cos he's working with the horses and - and other mens working on other different jobs.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 What kind of farm was it, was it a very big farm?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Yes, farm about between two and three hundred acres.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Is that an average farm for the ones you worked on?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Yes. About average today.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Did your parents share the same friends? Did your mother and father have the same friends or did they have different friends?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 The same friends. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Did your mother ever have friends of her own?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 No, not - not different from fa - father.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Did your father ever have friends of his won?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 No. They lived for one another in they days.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 You say friends weren't invited into the home as a rule?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 No. No. It wasn't - it wasn't like it was - the visiting like there is today. They can't live without they be happing to somebody today.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 So you can't remember friends ever calling in casually without any invitation?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 No. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Nor neighbours? Your parents didn't often go out visiting friends or neighbours, they'd just see them at the chapel?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 That's right. Yes. They had to content their self home in they days.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Apart from the chapel evenings did your parents ever go anywhere else to sort of play games or anything?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 
No, no, no, the only games us kid - us used to go when I used to go out with him odd times. You know, the same as I told you - trapping. That's al
l, father never-father never used to go to the games nor nothing like that, there wasn't nothing like that in they days.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 What would your mother do while you were out trapping?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Well mother stop home something with the fire, or knitting or sewing or something.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Did she ever get any materials to make up dresses from people?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 
People divide society into different classes or groups, in that time before 1918 did you think of some people belonging to one group and some to another?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 
Well, I know back in they days the - the - they used to be looked be sir and all that in they days but they don't do it today. It was more classy back in they days, than it's today. Used to have to touch your hat to 'em and bow to 'em nearly but they won'
t do that today.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 What do you think the different groups would be then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 
Well like 'tis now. I mean they - us be all human beings aint us. Of course that's - that's proper - that's back in the Tory days, I'm talking about. Proper Tory days then.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 What kind of people would there be? Who were these people you had to say sir to?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Well - one's who'd got houses or - farmers, they looked be called sir - in they day.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 How about shopkeepers?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Yes. Yes, sirs.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 What about the people who ran the chapel, what were they?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Oh they - they'm like yourself, you wouldn't call they sir. Without its a minister he'd look for be called sir.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Was the minister a local man? Where did he come from?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Who - oh the minister, well - you - you - you had to call ee sir. He feels he'd be better wouldn't he.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 
What group did you think of yourself as coming from? You said the minister and the schoolmaster, shopkeepers and farmers all expected to be called sir. What did you look on yourself as being, what group did you belong to?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Well you'd feel like you'd have to call 'em that. You know - you feel inside of you like you'd feel you'd have to call 'em, in they days.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Were you ever told to touch your cap or show respect?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 What group would you say you belonged to yourself?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 I couldn't say what group. I don't know see, what they call that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Can you remember being brought up to treat people of one sort differently from people of another?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 No. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Were you ever told to touch your cap or show respect in any way?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Was there anyone around the area you'd call sir or master or madam?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Who would that be?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 The ministers or - ladies you see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 What about shopkeepers?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Oh no, not they.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Would you ever have to lift your cap to people like the ministers?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Yes. Ministers, church ministers or - well - Methodist ministers - like. That's all you call sir.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Did you ever touch your cap to them, were you ever taught to do that?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Who were the most important people round Bovey Tracey and Oldertown? Who did you think were the most important people? In those days.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Well the - the people that had money you see. There wasn't no - I don't know no - important - peopl
e. The squires and that. See, the squires - landlords and that was the most important.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Were the farmers landlords?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 The - the landlords and the farmers that owned a lot of ground.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Was your farm cottage rented or did it go with the farm?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Go with the farm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Did the farmer ever come to look at it or inspect it at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 No, no, no. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Was the teacher called sir in those days?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 The teacher? Schoolteacher? Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 What sort of people would you say went to the church, do you know anything about that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Well - what sort of people. Well just ordinary people. Like we was go to the chapel.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 There was no real difference in the type of people that went?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 No. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Where you lived did all the people have the same standard of living?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Yes. In they days. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 There were no people who were really poor and some who were better off?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 No. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Do you think that any group felt superior to the rest? Amongst the labourers.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Were there any families who were thought of as rough and others as respectable?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 No, they was fair - fairly respectable, the farmers, in they days.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 What about farm workers, were they the same?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Yes, they - they - they was as well as they could be - under the circumstances.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Do you ever remember anything like gipsies?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Gipsies, there used to be a lot of gipsies come around then.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 What did people think about gipsies?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Well they was all right, they tell your fortune and all that, yes. They was all right.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Did they ever come asking for food or asking for work?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 
No, but - perhaps mother would give 'em a cup of tea or anything, you wouldn't - they wouldn't ask for it. Mother would give 'em to a - a bit of butter or anything like what was about. Cup of tea.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Did everyone treat them OK?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 No, I don't know about other people, no, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 
Do you remember a distinction of any kind between a craftsman and a labourer in those days? A skilled worker and a labourer, was there any sort of distinction made between those two do you remember?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 No, weren't no different.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Did your mother and father have the same attitude to people in different groups? Did they treat everybody the same?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Yes, yes, treat everybody the same.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Do yo
u think your mother saw herself as belonging to a particular social group at all? Do you think she was aware of being a member of a social group?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 No. No.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Do you think it was possible to move from one group to another at this time? From being a 
labourer to being a farmer, do you think it was possible to make this move?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Yes, well they was looked on as a little bit higher, the - the farmers, than what the working class was.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Were there any people who sort of worked their way up, from the working class to being a farmer?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 They couldn't work their self up then like they do today. They didn't have the money.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Did your father ever say anything about how he'd like to have a little farm of his own in those days?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 No. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Do you remember anyone being described as a real gentleman or a real lady?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Were you ever brought to sort of respect your elders?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Respect 'em? Yes. Had to in they days.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Who would tell you to do that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Well - father and mother. And the such - and the teachers at school.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Do you ever remember seeing a policeman around where you lived as a child?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Policeman? Yes, you used to see him round sometimes. In his beat.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Did he ever come to the house or anything like that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 No, not - no, I can - no - never need for him to then, in our affairs.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Your mother didn't ever say when you were naughty I'll call a policeman or anything like that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 No. Never had to do that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 How do you think the policeman treated the people in general?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 I couldn't say how big their beat was. Whoops, sorry.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Can you remember anybody ever saying anything about policemen?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 No. No, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 How did you get on with the farmer did you find him OK?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 The policeman?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 No, the farmer?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Oh he's all right if they go straight.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 What do you mean if they go straight?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 
Well I mean to say there was anything lying about what them borrowed and that the policeman would have 'em in they days. I mean cattle dead or anything and - left about and he should see it well they - they would get summonsed you see, in they days.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Who would get summonsed?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 The - the farmer. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Did this happen ever?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 No, I never knowed it to happen.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Your father and mother got on Ok with the farmer by and large?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 They used to get on all right with 'em.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Do you ever remember feeling that your parents had to struggle to make ends meet in those days?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Yes, they had to make ends meet in they days, 'cos the wages wasn't very much.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 What did you think about that? Do you remember ever thinking anything about it when you were young?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 No, couldn't - couldn't do no different. See there wasn't the money about then.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 What difference did it make to the family when your father was ill, or out of work?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 He was never out of work, father was never out of work, without he was sick.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 What would happen when he was ill?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Oh he was on the club. Get so much from the club. That's all, wasn't no state.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Who would bring that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 The man that belonged to the club.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Did he come to the house with the money?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 He come to the house with it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 How much did your father have to pay for this club?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Oh they get about ten shillings a week perhaps. From the club.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Did he pay every week into this club?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 So much every week, I can't remember what he had to pay. Contributions, I can't remember that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 You think most people contributed to clubs at this time?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Yes, I don't know what they pay. 'Cos I was in the club but I - I come out of him now. Haven't been in clubs years now. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Why was that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 
Well, 'cos - there's no need for them I mean you - you - you be - get the old age pension and - you know what I mean, you - you - you was paying it 'cos you get the doctor - if you'm old age pensioners you see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 In those days there wasn't anything like the old age pension and things was there?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Oh no, the - I mean, in they days old age pension wasn't much.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 So it was as well to join a club, for your father?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 They - yes, well they had to, they wouldn't get no other pay if they were sick you see. 'Cos they couldn't get it off the boss.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 What would happen did you say when it was raining in the fields?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Yes, well they had to stick out in that.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 You didn't get any money from the club then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 No, no. Oh no, not if it was raining. 'Cos he'd be in his work. He'd only get money from the club if he was sick.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Did you ever get help from the guardians or the parish?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 No, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Was your father ill very often?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 No, not very often, I can't remember very often.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Was there anyone in the district whom the people disapproved of very strongly?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 You can't remember anyone being made to leave the area?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 No. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 You don't remember anyone being made to leave by rough music?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 When you played while you were still at school did you ever have a yard, a back yard to play in?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 What about a garden, did you ever play in the garden at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Had a - I'd work in the garden with father.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 You didn't actually play in the garden?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Oh no, no, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 So you did help with the gardening?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 That's right, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Did you ever belong to any youth organizations?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 No, no, nothing like that in they days.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 If I could ask about home life after leaving school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Oh it's all right. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Did you continue to live at home when you went to start work?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Yes, yes, I still lived at home.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Do you think starting full time work changed your relationship with your parents at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Yes - made - made us better.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 In what way?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Well I mean, you - you - you was - getting a little bit you know. Money.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 What would happen when you were still at school, did they really have to fight hard?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Yes, did in they days.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 
Did they ever talk about what it was like, because there was just you at that time with your mother and father, did they ever talk about what it was like before you were born, when they had all the other brothers and sisters?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 No. No. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Did you spend Sunday any differently when you left school, did you still go to chapel Sunday school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Yes. Oh - not after - yes, before we went to Southbrook.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 How much of a difference was there between leaving school and going to Southbrook, how many months difference, or years?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 About twelve months.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 So you worked on the farm at Oldertown?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 I worked - at Oldertown for two - about twelve months. Then we went to Southbrook.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 You say you went to school from five years old to thirteen years old?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Yes.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 How many times did you have to change school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 I - I didn't change school at all. I was at - at the same school all the time. Never went to another school.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Even if your father moved around the area?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Was still in - still in Ilsington parish.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Did you still go to chapel?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Twice a day on Sunday?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Yes. Or once a day perhaps.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 You didn't go quite so often once you'd left school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 No, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Did you ever take any interests in politics at this time?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 No. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 So you didn't have any so-t of views on politics at this time?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 No. Nothing.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Did you ever vote in a general election before 1919?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 1919? No. No. 'Cos I wasn't old enough.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Did you ever feel afterwards any pressure to vote for a particular party, when you were old enough to vote?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Where to?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Were you ever made to feel, or did you ever feel that you had to vote for a particular political party because of pressure from someone?

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 No. In the Army I felt I had to go. When the war - was on.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 But you didn't in ordinary election times?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Were you ever a member of a political party?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Did you ever take part in any political activity other than at election times?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 You told me earlier how you spent your spare time, helping your father with the rabbit gins and mole gins?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 And doing bits of gardening?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 That's right.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Did 
this carry on after you left school? What did you do in your spare time after you left school when you were working full time with your father helping on the farm?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Oh - I used to then go round - killing rabbit traps and - and catching moles the same in the spare time that I had.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Did you ever do anything else?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 No. Only that, carry the milk.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Did you go out much in the evenings?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 No. It was too far from - anywhere. Weren't nothing doing out.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Did you ever go for long walks at this time?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Well, be meself like, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Where would you go to then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Well - there wasn't no houses, we could go for a walk in the fields or - the lanes, anywhere like.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 You were quite happy?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Did you ever make any new friends at this time, did you ever meet any new friends, boys or girls at this time?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 How did you get on with the other farm workers?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Only when I went school with 'em. And when I went - went to Southbrook I was all amongst strangers you see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 How did you find that, did you mind?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Oh I soon - after a time I - I picked up with my mates. You know, made friends with 'em.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Where did you meet them?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Down - Bovey Tracey, Southbrook, Bovey Tracey.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Would they be on the farm with you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Yes, yes, different places, in the potteries and - and quarries and one place and another used to work.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 When you were working in the quarries and potteries?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Where would you go with these friends then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Well go for walk or - go and as it - go in the village of a night or go in Newton Abbot of a Saturday night.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 What would you do there?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Go in the picture house. See the pictures.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 What was that like in those days?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Well - yes, yes, well, used to see living
 pictures too. Used - used to go from Bovey to Newton nearly every Saturday night. Get home by twelve o'clock - Sunday morning, half past twelve. Used to push bike.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 You had a bike then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Yes. Push bike then, six mile each way.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 When did you get your pushbike?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Father bought it when I was about fourteen, fifteen. Bought it in Halfords in Newton. Four pound fourteen and sixpence he paid for it.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 That would make a complete difference to the way of life really, to be able to ride around?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 That's lovely job to have a bicycle in they days.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 You usually went out on Saturday evening rather than during the week, I suppose in the week you'd be working?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 I should be working in the week.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 What else did you do in Newton Abbott, did you always to the cinema or would you go a pub or something?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 
No, pubs, I never went to pubs much, they never worried me. No, I was never in public houses. No. I used to like a smoke, you know, cigarette. But public houses never worried me.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 What about your friends?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Some - well they used to go in but I didn't used to go in.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 
Do you remember any fairs or anything after you left school? Were there any fairs in Newton Abbot? Fairs or travelling shows or circuses or anything?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Nothing like that even after you left school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 No. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Did your parents meet your friends? Did your mother and father meet your new friends?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Yes. The neighbours, they're in and out if they should run against 'em.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Did they expect to know where you were when you went out with them?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 No, they would - never worry.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 They didn't say you'd got to be in by a certain time?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 No. I should know that meself. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 Did you have any sort of girlfriends round this time?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 No, no, only what I went school with, that's all. You know, friends.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 
I suppose leaving the area and going to Southbook that was a long way away so would you still keep in touch with the friends you had before?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 No, that's too far away then. Three mile
 or more you see. A lost 'em all then. And I had to make me fresh friends - when I went to Bovey Tracey, see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 How far is it from Southbrook to Bovey Tracey?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 It's about a mile from the village or town.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6242707 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 You said you had a bicycle when you were fourteen, did many of your other friends have bicycles?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644173 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16389910\charrsid9705256 No, I left they behind.
